load ../infoflow-coord-carriage.maude

--- ============================ COVERAGE ======================================

--- Coverage: under explicit `shared`, A's consume can reach B's observed
--- `remaining` outcome.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  shared(counter) consume(wfA, counter) observeRemaining(wfB, counter)
  =>* C:Cfg outcomeRead(wfA, wfB, counter, remaining) .

--- Coverage: under explicit `shared`, A's acquire can reach B's observed
--- `holders` outcome.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  shared(lease) acquire(wfA, lease) observeHolders(wfB, lease)
  =>* C:Cfg outcomeRead(wfA, wfB, lease, holders) .

--- Coverage: the inbound integrity gate catches an untrusted workflow writing a
--- high-integrity coordination resource.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  resourceIntegrity(counter, hi) workflowIntegrity(wfA, lo) consume(wfA, counter)
  =>* C:Cfg coordInjection .

--- Coverage: the outbound read gate catches a private coordination outcome flowing
--- to a public sink.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  resourceReaders(counter, hi) sinkClearance(wfB, lo)
  outcomeRead(wfA, wfB, counter, remaining)
  =>* C:Cfg outcomeLeak .

--- ============================ BITE ==========================================

--- Bite: under the default partition, A's consume never reaches B's `remaining`.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  partitioned(counter) consume(wfA, counter) observeRemaining(wfB, counter)
  =>* C:Cfg outcomeRead(wfA, wfB, counter, remaining) .

--- Bite: under the default partition, A's acquire never reaches B's `holders`.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  partitioned(lease) acquire(wfA, lease) observeHolders(wfB, lease)
  =>* C:Cfg outcomeRead(wfA, wfB, lease, holders) .

--- Bite: a trusted workflow writing a high-integrity coordination resource does
--- not inject.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  resourceIntegrity(counter, hi) workflowIntegrity(wfA, hi) consume(wfA, counter)
  =>* C:Cfg coordInjection .

--- Bite: a private coordination outcome flowing to a private-cleared sink does not
--- leak.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-INFOFLOW-COORD-CARRIAGE :
  resourceReaders(counter, hi) sinkClearance(wfB, hi)
  outcomeRead(wfA, wfB, counter, remaining)
  =>* C:Cfg outcomeLeak .
